      • getPosition

        int getPosition()
        Returns the position of this pagereffolder in menu order of the parent folder. The position is only related to other pagereffolders in the parent. Use StoreElement.getChildIndex(de.espirit.firstspirit.access.store.StoreElement) to get the absolute index in child list
        Returns:
        position in the menu order of the parent or -1
        Since:
